alias msgfuct {
  set %i 0
  set %icount 0
  :start
  inc %i
  if ($snick(#,%i) != $null) {
    if ($snick(#,%i) != $me) {
      .timer 1 %i .msg $snick(#,%i) %tmpfuct
      inc %icount
    }
    goto start
    else { halt }
  }
  echo -a %beg %gadast 15Total 14Nicks 15Messaged14 %icount 15! | unset %i %icount %tmpfuct
}
alias msgnick {
  if (%gircfile == $null) { echo -a %beg %gadast 15You 14Don't 15Have A 14Nick File 15! | halt }
  else {
    if ($exists(%gircfile) == $true) {
      set %x 0
      set %xcount 0 
      set %xx 1
      write -c tmp.txt -
      :start
      inc %x
      if ($snick($chan,%x) != $null) {
        if ($snick($chan,%x) != $me) {
          :redo
          set %tempnick $read %gircfile
          set %tmp.c $read -w $+ $chr(42) $+ %tempnick $+ $chr(42) tmp.txt
          if (%tempnick != %tmp.c) {
            write tmp.txt %tempnick
          }
          if (%tempnick == %tmp.c) {
            goto redo
          }
          if (%tempnick !ison $chan) {
            .timer5 $+ %xx 1 %xx .msg $snick($chan,%x) nick %tempnick 
            inc %xcount
            inc %xx
          }
          if (%tempnick ison $chan) {
            dec %x
          }
        }
        goto start
        else { halt }
      }
      echo -a %beg %gadast 15Total 14Nicks 15Messaged14 %xcount 15! | unset %x %xx %xcount %tempnick %rcrname %rcrlenght %tmp.c
    }
    else { echo -a %beg %gadast 15The Nick File �(14 $+ %gircfile $+ 15) Doesn't Exist ! | halt }
  }
}
alias msgnickw {
  if (%gircfile == $null) { echo -a %beg %gadast 15You 14Don't 15Have A 14Nick File 15! | halt }
  else {
    if ($exists(%gircfile) == $true) {
      set %rcrname $$?="Which b0t?" | set %rcrlenght $len(%rcrname)
      set %x 0
      set %xcount 0 
      set %xx 1
      write -c tmp.txt -
      :start
      inc %x
      if ($nick($chan,%x) != $null) {
        if (($nick($chan,%x) != $me) && ($left($nick($chan,%x),%rcrlenght) == %rcrname)) {
          :redo
          set %tempnick $read %gircfile
          set %tmp.c $read -w $+ $chr(42) $+ %tempnick $+ $chr(42) tmp.txt
          if (%tempnick != %tmp.c) {
            write tmp.txt %tempnick
          }
          if (%tempnick == %tmp.c) {
            goto redo
          }
          if (%tempnick !ison $chan) {
            .timer5 $+ %xx 1 %xx .msg $nick($chan,%x) nick %tempnick 
            inc %xcount
            inc %xx
          }
          if (%tempnick ison $chan) {
            dec %x
          }
        }
        goto start
        else { halt }
      }
      echo -a %beg %gadast 15Total 14Nicks 15Messaged14 %xcount 15! | unset %x %xx %xcount %tempnick %rcrname %rcrlenght %tmp.c
    }
    else { echo -a %beg %gadast 15The Nick File �(14 $+ %gircfile $+ 15) Doesn't Exist ! | halt }
  }
}
alias nickfile {
  if (%gircfile != $null) {
    if ($exists(%gircfile) == $true) { .run %gircfile | halt }
    else { write -c %gircfile | .run %gircfile | halt }
  }
  else { set %gircfile $$?="Enter The Name Of The Nick File" | write -c %gircfile | .run %gircfile | halt }
}
